data.description: Check out this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom move-in ready home in South Bossier's Savannah Place Subdivision.  This home offers both style and practicality. Neutral-colored paint throughout, a kitchen pantry, breakfast bar, eat-in kitchen makes this floorplan design for easy living. Step outside to the covered patio, adding a perfect space to relax or entertain. This home, with it's fenced yard, no carpet, kitchen island, and covered patio, is a complete package. Make it yours today! Close to Barksdale Air Force Base (BAFB), Shopping, Dinning, and more.
